e keeping tabs on a lightweight like myself then they are doing the same and more to others this is more than supposition as i know of other nuj members on the database the following year thomas and five journalists and photographers who had also been under surveillance by the london metropolitan police services national domestic extremism and disorder intelligence unit ndediu began legal action against the force the ndedius reports obtained by thomas described him as a general rabble rouser and alleged comedian and stated mark thomas stops has quantity of cress on rear of his cycle he told the independents adam lusher the polices powers of observation are to be admired i did indeed have cress on my bike but is it really suitable to spend taxpayers money observing the movement of cress televisionedit friday night live channel   saturday zoo channel   viva cabaret channel   denton channel  australia  the mark thomas comedy product later renamed the mark thomas product channel  which ran for six series totalling  episodes – dispatches the lie of the land channel   thomas country channel   the immigration and asylum bill channel   secret map of britain channel   dispatches mark thomas — broom cupboard inspector channel   dispatches mark thomas — debt collector channel   dispatches after school arms club channel   dispatches mark thomas on coca cola channel   radioedit the mary whitehouse experience radio   the mix radio   sleeping with the nme radio   loose talk radio  – booked radio  – celluloid psychiatrists radio   left bank of the mind radio   mark thomas presents… radio   shows on stan freberg the firesign theatre shelley berman and mort sahl chain reaction radio   my life in serious organised crime radio   ramblings radio   walking the ridgeway track in wiltshire and oxfordshire mark thomas the manifesto radio  –present bravo figaro radio   discographyedit sex filth and religion video  live  dambusters  the night war broke out  mark thomas comedy show dvd  mark t